# Aurora Design System — dircolors
# Palette: cyan #29b6f6→39, cyan-strong #67cbfa→117, violet #a78bfa→141,
#          rose #f9a8c4→218, text-muted #a7bcc9→110, success #7dd3c7→116,
#          warn #c6a36b→179, error #c78490→181, text-primary #e6f4fb→195

TERM xterm-256color
TERM xterm-truecolor
TERM screen-256color
TERM tmux-256color
TERM rxvt-unicode-256color

